11. There is a constraint definition: MassLimitRequirement.
12. MassLimitRequirement has input: measuredMass : Real.
13. MassLimitRequirement has input: limit : Real.
14. MassLimitRequirement constraint: measuredMass <= limit.
15. There is an action definition: PerformWeighing.
16. PerformWeighing has input: operator : TestOperator.
17. PerformWeighing has input: equipment : WeighingEquipment.
18. PerformWeighing has input: vehicle : Vehicle.
19. PerformWeighing has output: measuredMass : Real.
20. There is an action definition: DetermineCompliance.
21. DetermineCompliance has input: measuredMass : Real.
22. DetermineCompliance has input: limit : Real.
23. DetermineCompliance has output: isCompliant : Boolean.

26. VehicleTestCase has part: vehicle : Vehicle.
27. VehicleTestCase has part: operator : TestOperator.

31. ComplianceTestCampaign has attribute: limitKilograms = 2500.0.
32. ComplianceTestCampaign has part: testCases : VehicleTestCase[*].

40. vehicleA.vehicle has attribute complianceStatus = "Pending".
41. vehicleA has part operator : TestOperator redefines operator.
42. vehicleA.operator has attribute name = "Operator-1".
43. vehicleA has part equipment : WeighingEquipment redefines equipment.
44. vehicleA.equipment has attribute manufacturer = "CertifiedScaleCo".
45. campaign.testCases[2] is vehicleB : VehicleTestCase redefines testCases[2].
46. vehicleB has attribute limitKilograms = campaign.limitKilograms.
47. vehicleB has part vehicle : Vehicle redefines vehicle.
48. vehicleB.vehicle has attribute identifier = "Vehicle-B".
49. vehicleB.vehicle has attribute actualMassKilograms = 2600.0.
50. vehicleB.vehicle has attribute complianceStatus = "Pending".
51. vehicleB has part operator : TestOperator redefines operator.
52. vehicleB.operator has attribute name = "Operator-2".
53. vehicleB has part equipment : WeighingEquipment redefines equipment.
54. vehicleB.equipment has attribute manufacturer = "CertifiedScaleCo".

**E. Actions for Each Test Case**
55. There is an action weighingVehicleA : PerformWeighing.
56. weighingVehicleA has in operator = campaign.testCases.vehicleA.operator.
57. weighingVehicleA has in equipment = campaign.testCases.vehicleA.equipment.
58. weighingVehicleA has in vehicle = campaign.testCases.vehicleA.vehicle.
59. weighingVehicleA has out measuredMass = campaign.testCases.vehicleA.vehicle.actualMassKilograms.
60. There is an action weighingVehicleB : PerformWeighing.
61. weighingVehicleB has in operator = campaign.testCases.vehicleB.operator.
62. weighingVehicleB has in equipment = campaign.testCases.vehicleB.equipment.
63. weighingVehicleB has in vehicle = campaign.testCases.vehicleB.vehicle.
64. weighingVehicleB has out measuredMass = campaign.testCases.vehicleB.vehicle.actualMassKilograms.
65. There is an action complianceVehicleA : DetermineCompliance.
66. complianceVehicleA has in measuredMass = campaign.testCases.vehicleA.vehicle.actualMassKilograms.
67. complianceVehicleA has in limit = campaign.limitKilograms.
68. complianceVehicleA has out isCompliant = true.
69. There is an action complianceVehicleB : DetermineCompliance.
70. complianceVehicleB has in measuredMass = campaign.testCases.vehicleB.vehicle.actualMassKilograms.
71. complianceVehicleB has in limit = campaign.limitKilograms.
72. complianceVehicleB has out isCompliant = false.

**F. Requirements**
73. There is a requirement definition: 'MassComplianceRequirement'.
74. MassComplianceRequirement has text: "Verify that each measured vehicle mass is less than or equal to the 2,500 kilogram limit; otherwise mark the vehicle as non-compliant."
75. There is a requirement definition: 'SequentialTestingRequirement'.
76. SequentialTestingRequirement has text: "Support automated, sequential weighing of multiple vehicles using operators and certified equipment, recording each result for compliance management."
